  • R: ratio of enrichment
  • rawP: p value from hypergeometric test
  • adjP: p value adjusted by the multiple test adjustment
Finally, genes in the gene set are listed. For each gene, the table lists the user uploaded ID and value (optional), Entrez ID, Ensembl Gene Stable ID, Gene symbol, and description. Ensembl Gene Stable ID and Entrez Gene ID are linked to the Ensembl and Entrez Gene databases, respectively.
